{"tid":1511452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［全裸搜身］ 警司：同事無要求事主完全脫去內衣服","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T01:56:49.000Z","uid":291892,"like":21,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c818e0c738a7b944c91b8e6df7557c9c1be984af","tid":1511452,"uid":291892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:10:15.000Z","msg":"【警方例行記者會】支援科警司 #戚夏瑜 主動提起上星期關於被女示威者被全裸搜身事件的記者會，並指已翻查警員記事冊和閉路電視等資料，#確認 並非如女事主所說。當日搜身級別不需要完全脫去內衣服。<br />\n<br />\n她指根據 #警員記事冊，同事無要求事主完全脫去內衣服，無用任何物件指或拍打事主身體，沒有要求張開雙腿或踎低起身，因同事認為沒有需要。<br />\n<br />\nMadam戚 另稱搜身過程約4分鐘，不是事主所稱 15 - 30分鐘。另外，翻查走廊閉路電視片段，當時並沒有10多名警員在搜身室外。<br />\n<br />\n她指事主如有不滿，可作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n女事主記者會 - 全裸搜身過程：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103602823372112/posts/896956090703444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103602823372112%2Fposts%2F896956090703444&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=9aee5956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103602823372112/posts/896956090703444</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: journesis  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6sXd14a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6sXd14a.jpg&h=3343ba25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來人地蒙左面都知道事主係邊個 <br />\n仲可以翻查到當日閉路電視知道係4分鐘<br />\n有冇記者可以問下點解佢又知既 好叻叻呀<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"bdef9d6689c5ff671e579859fe109c923e881697","tid":1511452,"uid":197424,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"又肥又醜又黑心 咁都仲唔信報應？"},{"pid":"3bb7bcb00c53a1b68e19f4c8f806c919e0378280","tid":1511452,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"繼續吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ed44b9f8214376f48c35573eab82447fa89e57","tid":1511452,"uid":134226,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"on99<br />\n做咗就唔會寫出嚟啦<br />\n況且班狗落口供都寫啲唔寫啲㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcca7cc6cac6c7d8a0404784d8ec5fdf85a5a57","tid":1511452,"uid":291892,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講大話都醒啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係又一次比自己智商出賣</span>"},{"pid":"2d36039561fecb4c305a194ced099404a91e3073","tid":1511452,"uid":184379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"無要求，但有恐嚇"},{"pid":"ffd745a6e2c40580529777d73b74882c7f7b0519","tid":1511452,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c818e0c738a7b944c91b8e6df7557c9c1be984af","tid":1511452,"uid":291892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:10:15.000Z","msg":"【警方例行記者會】支援科警司 #戚夏瑜 主動提起上星期關於被女示威者被全裸搜身事件的記者會，並指已翻查警員記事冊和閉路電視等資料，#確認 並非如女事主所說。當日搜身級別不需要完全脫去內衣服。<br />\n<br />\n她指根據 #警員記事冊，同事無要求事主完全脫去內衣服，無用任何物件指或拍打事主身體，沒有要求張開雙腿或踎低起身，因同事認為沒有需要。<br />\n<br />\nMadam戚 另稱搜身過程約4分鐘，不是事主所稱 15 - 30分鐘。另外，翻查走廊閉路電視片段，當時並沒有10多名警員在搜身室外。<br />\n<br />\n她指事主如有不滿，可作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n女事主記者會 - 全裸搜身過程：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103602823372112/posts/896956090703444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103602823372112%2Fposts%2F896956090703444&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=9aee5956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103602823372112/posts/896956090703444</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: journesis  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6sXd14a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6sXd14a.jpg&h=3343ba25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來人地蒙左面都知道事主係邊個 <br />\n仲可以翻查到當日閉路電視知道係4分鐘<br />\n有冇記者可以問下點解佢又知既 好叻叻呀<br />\n</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"Push"